  "frontCover": "Front cover of a greeting card in a dramatic, noir-inspired digital illustration style. The background is a deep, moody blue, creating a sense of mystery. Dominating the center is a sleek, black cat silhouette wearing thick, round, dark-rimmed glasses, giving it an intellectual and serious demeanor. The cat is holding a single, lit birthday candle in its paw, held aloft as if for illumination. In front of the cat, tilted slightly, is a piece of yellowed paper with the bold, dark text \"TOP SECRET\" at the top, underlined by a thin red line. Below that, in a smaller, sans-serif font, is the text \"The Perfect Gift\". The overall mood is humorous and intriguing, playing on the idea of a secret investigation for a gift. The lighting is dramatic, with the candle flame casting a warm glow on the cat's face and the \"TOP SECRET\" document, creating strong shadows and highlights. The text \"A Birthday Investigation\" is displayed prominently at the top in a classic serif font, cream-colored with a subtle shadow, completing the thematic presentation. The composition is tightly focused on the cat and the document, with no other elements present, emphasizing the 'investigation' theme."
